proposals to reduce the 120000 us troops stationed in the 
pacific rim by 10 to 12 percent that would amount to a possible 
cut of 5000 military personnel from japan alone 
about 50000 us marines sailors soldiers and air force 
personnel are based in japan and okinawa 
