to the 7 billion cost of maintaining us forces here 
the lack of specifics about numbers is a negotiating tactic one 
us official said noting that the japanese understand our 
requirements and are willing to increase their financial support 
for such things as recreational facilities and hospitals to help 
us troops and their families 
in south korea and asia the americans are looking to the host 
