desecration charges and that is what she did in holding the law 
unconstitutional 
the flag desecration and destruction of property counts each 
carry a maximum penalty of one year in prison and a 100000 fine 
prosecutors were meeting to decide whether to take the remaining 
count of property destruction to trial or take the issue directly 
to the supreme court 
