national day of remembrance of the armenian genocide of 
19151923 
by a 4949 vote the senate refused to break a filibuster 
against doles resolution dole needed 60 votes to end the debate 
over three days opponents of the measure led by sen robert 
byrd dwva had filibustered the resolution 
despite doles defeat the measure is not dead in fact dole 
said he would ask for another cloture vote to be held next week 
two republicans took opposite positions on the resolution debate 
today 
