<TEXT>
the mighty microbe strikes again 
five fearless astronauts and the worlds very best spacecraft 
were poised this week to rocket into orbit with a spy satellite 
that might be vital to the nations security 
nasa the powerful technological force that conquered the moon 
and sent craft soaring toward distant stars had done everything 
possible to prepare for the cloakanddagger mission an army of 
engineers and technicians had given their best and were standing 
by awaiting the final countdown 
then the microbe came along 
some bug so small that even a microscope might not find it 
had somehow invaded the pristine premises of americas space 
program and struck down one of the nations best 
atlantis commander john o creighton nasa said had developed 
a sore throat and congestion it hurt to swallow and the nose was 
all stuffy 
if he were on television creighton would have been the 
before portrait in some cold medicine commercial if he were a 
6th grader mom would have kept him home 
but creighton is an astronaut about ready to take the controls 
in a 1 billion spacecraft carrying a half billiondollar payload 
and when an astronaut crewman gets sick everybody stays at home 
the mission was postponed twice and wont go now before saturday 
its happened before to nasa in 1969 apollo 9 was delayed for 
three days while the threeman crew recovered from the sniffles 
a year later nasa doctors learned that apollo 13 astronaut 
thomas k mattingly had been exposed to the measles another mean 
little microbe mattingly was removed from the flight and backup 
pilot john swigert was put on board as it turned out the apollo 
13 crew almost died when an oxygen tank exploded and mattingly 
safe at home never developed the measles 
nasa may do technological marvels and accomplish feats of wonder 
in outer space but it still hasnt conquered the mighty microbe 
the agency tries astronauts preparing for a mission are 
isolated for a week before launch nasa posts warnings about the 
isolation and takes pains to make sure that anyone but close family 
wears a mask around the crew members 
during the apollo program the isolation was even stricter a 
nasa doctor caused the cancellation of plans to have president 
nixon have dinner with the apollo 11 astronauts before the launch 
of that first moonlanding mission 
