satellite the bs2k was built by us company general electrics 
aerospace division to direct broadcasting for japans national nhk 
network 
the other a superbird b was built by ford aerospace to channel 
telephone telegraph and telex messages it was owned by 
mitsubishis subsidiary space communications corp 
