<TEXT>
the food and drug administration today 
approved a lowcalorie fat substitute made from milk and eggwhite 
proteins for use in frozen desserts 
the product called simplesse and described as an all 
natural fat substitute is manufactured by the nutrasweet co it 
is designed to have the taste and texture of fat but with fewer 
than half the calories 
the first product to be made with simplesse will be a frozen 
dairy dessert called simple pleasures which the company said has 
the creamy taste of ice cream but with significantly reduced 
calories and cholesterol 
the fda approved the companys petition to affirm that the food 
additive is generally recognized as safe 
simplesse is approved for use in frozen dessert products only 
the company would have to get further fda approval to use it in 
other foods said fda spokesman jeff nesbit 
nutrasweet a subsidiary of st louisbased monsanto co also 
developed aspartame the artificial sweetener marketed under the 
name nutrasweet 
the fda approved simplesse for use as a thickener or texturizer 
in frozen dessert products simplesse contains proteins from egg 
whites or milk or a combination of both 
foods containing simplesse will have to include the product on 
their labels because some people are allergic to eggs or milk or 
both the fda said 
simplesse has also been approved for marketing in west germany 
the united kingdom switzerland japan belgium the netherlands 
and luxembourg 
the fda is reviewing a petition from kraft inc seeking approval 
for the use in frozen desserts of a fat substitute made from egg 
whites and milk proteins 
also under review is a petition from proctor amp gamble co which 
wants to use a sucrose polyester called olestra as a partial 
subsitute for fats and oils in shortenings salad oils and cooking 
in the home and by the food service industry 
lisa lefferts staff scientist at the center for science in the 
public interest said the group has no safety concerns about 
simplesse however the group has recommended that the fda monitor 
the impact of products such as simplesse on the american diet 
will we eat more and more doubledip ice creams and eat less 
nutritious foods or will they help us lower our fat intake we 
dont really know lefferts said 
the company said simple pleasures will be introduced in 
chocolate strawberry rum raisin coffe peach and toffee crunch 
and other flavors would be added later 
as an example the company said simple pleasures strawberry 
contains 120 calories and one gram of fat per fourounce serving 
compared with 250 calories and 15 grams of fat for the same amount 
of a leading superpremium brand 
monsantos stock surged as word of the fda approval circulated 
on wall street rising 437 in early trading to 11225 a share 
on the new york stock exchange 
